data.description: Welcome to easy living at Maple Villas! Enjoy the maintenance free lifestyle in this 2 bedroom, 2 bath, with a den. The open floor plan makes it easy to navigate, and great for entertaining. Featuring two outdoor living spaces, lots of natural light, and convenient to walking/ running path for exercise. Master bath was recently updated with a Kohler hydrotherapy tub, making it easy to relax in the spa tub. Master bath has double sinks, wide doorway, and has fully functioning shower in addition to the Kohler walk-in bath. Ceiling fans, blinds, and new water heater were recently added. Great neighborhood and location provide convenience for shopping and dining. Yard, landscaping, snow removal, and more are included in your quarterly dues. Quarterly dues may be less than other no/low maintenance communities nearby. Come see this one quickly!   Seller has a VA Assumable Mortgage (Rate 2.75%) for those that qualify, you do not need to be a veteran.
